    <h1 class="opener__hed  opener__hed--light opener__hed--small" >        The Story of One Mississippi County Shows How Private Schools Are Exacerbating Segregation
    </h1>

    
            <div class="article-meta-1  article-meta-1--light">
            <span class="article-meta-1__byline">
                by <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/jennifer-berry-hawes">Jennifer Berry Hawes</a>, data analysis by <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/nat-lash">Nat Lash</a>, with additional reporting by <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/mollie-simon">Mollie Simon</a>            </span>
            <time class="article-meta-1__pubdate">
                <time class="timestamp" datetime="2024-12-19EST06:00">Dec. 19, 6 a.m. EST</time>
            </time>
        </div>
    
    </div> <!-- Close .opener__topic-title-dek-wrapper -->

            <div class="content"> <!-- not sure if this is the best way to reestablish the text column -->
            <h2 class="opener__dek opener__dek--match-text-column" style="display: none">                A new ProPublica analysis shows a stark pattern across states in the Deep South: Alongside majority-Black public school districts, a separate web of private academies are filled almost entirely with white students.
            </h2>
        </div>
    
</div>
        
<div class="article-meta-1
     article-meta-1--left      article-meta-1--hide-byline " data-pp-location="article meta">

    <span class="article-meta-1__byline" data-pp-location="article byine">
        by <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/jennifer-berry-hawes">Jennifer Berry Hawes</a>, data analysis by <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/nat-lash">Nat Lash</a>, with additional reporting by <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/mollie-simon">Mollie Simon</a>    </span>
    <time class="article-meta-1__pubdate">
        <time class="timestamp" datetime="2024-12-19EST06:00">Dec. 19, 6 a.m. EST</time>
    </time>

