&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=1500&amp;q=75&amp;w=2000&amp;s=8809632ef33c81bca6cd7bc85fcaa28b 2000w"
