    <div class="story-card__description">
                        <a class="story-card__series" href="https://www.propublica.org/series/segregation-academies">Segregation Academies</a>
        
        <h3 class="story-card__hed" >
            <a href="https://www.propublica.org/article/segregation-academies-school-voucher-money-north-carolina">
                                    Segregation Academies Across the South Are Getting Millions in Taxpayer Dollars
                            </a>
        </h3>

        <p class="story-card__dek" >
                            North Carolina offers an especially telling window into what is happening across this once legally segregated region where legislatures are now rapidly expanding and adopting controversial voucher-style programs.
                    </p>

        <p class="story-card__byline">
            by <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/jennifer-berry-hawes">Jennifer Berry Hawes</a> and <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/mollie-simon">Mollie Simon</a>,             <time class="timestamp" datetime="2024-11-18EST05:00">Nov. 18, 5 a.m. EST</time>
